obo:GO_0003674  a  owl:Class .

gomodel:SYNGO_610  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: 374 different proteins that copurify with a PSD fraction where identfied by LC-MS/MS.\nRS15_RAT was found among these proteins.\nFor proteins coming from datasets derived from PSD (detergent-resistant synaptic junctions) preparations without defined selection / enrichment of the pre- or postsynaptic compartment we cannot assign these proteins to excitatory and/or inhibitory nor to the presynapse or / and postsynapse without further information.. Experimental description: \"PSD fractions were prepared from rat forebrains largely as previously described (4, 9).\" p. 21004\n\n8/8/2017 Pim\n- Proteomics database search returned human RL15 protein, but this is a problem with the data base search configuration." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
